        Dependencies
        ============
        
        1. openpyxl
        2. pyexcel-io >= 0.0.8
        
        .. testcode::
           :hide:
        
           >>> import os
           >>> os.unlink("your_file.xlsx")
           >>> os.unlink("another_file.xlsx")
        
